{"tid":422392,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"影閃卡到底有冇問題?","createTime":"2017-10-03T04:19:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-03T10:28:46.000Z","uid":97162,"like":12,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"07954782476a02099160ebbd02fa4f5c8d113077","tid":422392,"uid":97162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T04:19:56.000Z","msg":"見愈黎愈多女人分手之後啲閃卡比人通街派就黎喊苦喊忽，好撚慘好要人同情咁<br />\n又話乜信佢先比佢，又話情趣黎好撚正常<br />\n但講真家下個個上網唔開名唔洗責任<br />\n今日唔知聽日事，一個唔該分左手點解仲要比面你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n人地派你就一定唔岩架喇，但你自己都唔保護自己怪得邊個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 樓主守舊影閃卡好正常但風險自己承擔<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 根本唔應該影女仔要保護自己"},{"pid":"89cce6c0b24db4132fc5eb43539ae12c29e5ae6d","tid":422392,"uid":75583,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T04:27:49.000Z","msg":"影之前三思果個係咪一個散咗都唔會流出你d閃卡嘅男人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0c0e4dc20d60ff7c0d307fc2079841fc48c60e4","tid":422392,"uid":97162,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T04:33:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>影之前三思果個係咪一個散咗都唔會流出你d閃卡嘅男人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n影得個刻都好信任對方覺得唔會架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n結果咪又一大堆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf9e5178d02fa0a3051e88f4c4e7df152591c1cb","tid":422392,"uid":21028,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T04:38:38.000Z","msg":"情趣黎 唔影大家邊有趣"},{"pid":"bddd48a0b128ea0e4e9cc3042de0c75cec54902b","tid":422392,"uid":97162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T04:43:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>情趣黎 唔影大家邊有趣</blockquote><br />\n但有機會流出喎會唔會考慮其他情趣去保障自己?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />